            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="non-tech">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dqlxklbcq/image/upload/v1718858488/graph_non-tech_qfquad.gif"></img>
            <div class="watch-out">
                <h1>◀️ We have these course ,Learn these course ▶️</h1>
                <div class="watch-out-btn">
                    <button class="btn btn-warning non-tech-btn"><a href="/course/marketing">Learn Digital Marketing
